{"type": "article", "id": 4583, "title": "Orbits 时钟", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-22T07:56:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052337493wkAhP1G7Mz0RfXJ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tStudio Ve 设计工作室最近带来一款名为「Orbits Clock」的新作。在其至简的黑色钟面上，并没有我们常见的时针、分针以及秒针，而是代之以 3 个立体的黑色圆环，设计团队的灵感来源于原子的核式结构，选用超轻的碳纤维材质制作圆环，而从小到大的 3 个圆环分别代表了秒针、分针与时针，凭借石英机芯而驱动，给人一种时光变幻的印象。定价 150 美元，<a href=\"http://www.studiove.com/collections/shop/products/orbits-clock\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"http://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0212/7228/products/OR-BK-_1_1024x1024.gif?v=1418918529\" width=\"640\" alt=\"\"><img src=\"http://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0212/7228/products/OR-BK-_2_1024x1024.gif?v=1418918531\" width=\"640\" alt=\"\"><img src=\"http://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0212/7228/products/OR-BK-_4_1024x1024.gif?v=1418918532\" width=\"640\" alt=\"\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233746HbSik64MRtsoE3pg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233747xOnrtJ8sbDVmFSIP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233748xHwIOcQJ7jdRsFSr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}